with version stable 1.1
with base    libXScrnSaver
with role    graphic
with trait   x11
with source  http://www.linuxpages.org/download/rsaver-$VERSION.tar.bz2
with info    good 20120703
with info    last 20050320
with info    home http://www.linuxpages.org/rsaver_en.php
with info    cite 'simple X screensaver that only uses Xlib
After a specified amount of time it
will start to draw radioactive signs.
If a timeout is not specified, the
timeout value is obtained from the X server.'

build(){
make &&
make install PREFIX=/usr DESTDIR=$DESTDIR
}
